def myargmax(vector, excludes):
    imax = None
    nmax = -100000000
    for i in range(0, len(vector)):
        if i in excludes: continue
        if vector[i] > nmax:
            nmax = vector[i]
            imax = i
    return imax

class UCBAgent:
    
    def __init__(self, objects, delta):
        
        self.objects = objects # all possible objects
        
        self.X_all = []
        for o in self.objects:
            self.X_all.append(o.features)
                        
        self.X_idx = [] # Past trials (index)
        self.X = [] # Past trials (feature)
        self.T = [] # Past obervations
        
        self.mus = []
        self.sigmas = []
        
        self.beta = 0.0
        self.delta = delta
        
        self.mu = np.array([0. for _ in range(len(objects))])
        self.sigma = np.array([0.5 for _ in range(len(objects))])

    def argmax_ucb(self):
        t = len(self.T) + 1
        K = len(self.objects)
        self.beta = math.log(K * t * t / self.delta)
        
        scores = self.mu + self.sigma * np.sqrt(self.beta)
        imax = myargmax(scores, self.X_idx) # Do not propose again if it already runs

        #imax = myargmax(scores, []) # Do not propose again if it already runs
        
        if imax == None: 
            return None
        
        self.proposed_score = scores[imax]
        
        return imax
    
    def propose_next(self):
        self.proposed = self.argmax_ucb()
    
    def execute(self, is_served = True):
        if is_served:
            x = self.objects[self.proposed].features
            t = self.objects[self.proposed].observe()
            self.X_idx.append(self.proposed)
            
            self.X.append(x)
            self.T.append(t)                    # Observe
            
            self.mus.append(self.mu)
            self.sigmas.append(self.sigma)
    
            gp = GaussianProcessRegressor()    # Update mu and sigma
            gp.fit(self.X, self.T)
            self.mu, self.sigma = gp.predict(self.X_all, return_std=True)

    class Coordinate:
        def __init__(self, x, y, v):
            self.features = np.array([x, y])
            self.value = v

        def observe(self):
            return self.value
        
    objects = []
    for x in np.arange(-3, 3, 0.25):
        for y in np.arange(-3, 3, 0.25):
            v = np.sin(x) + np.cos(y)
            objects.append(Coordinate(x, y, v))
            

    from mpl_toolkits.mplot3d import Axes3D
    fig = plt.figure()

    ucb = UCBAgent(objects, 0.1)
    for i in range(0, 10):
        ucb.propose_next()
        ucb.execute(True)
        
        ax = Axes3D(fig)
        ax.scatter(
            map(lambda o: o.features[0], objects),
            map(lambda o: o.features[1], objects),
            map(lambda o: o.observe(), objects))

class MultiUCBAgent:
    
    def __init__(self, agents):
        self.agents = agents
        self.n_agents = len(agents)
        self.t = 0
        self.choosen_idx = None
    
    def execute(self):
        
        if self.t < 2 * self.n_agents: # first two rounds, do round robin
            agent = self.agents[self.t % self.n_agents]
            agent.propose_next()
            agent.execute(True)
        else:        
            V = {}
            for agent in self.agents:
                agent.propose_next()
                if agent.proposed != None:
                    V[agent] = math.sqrt(agent.beta) * agent.sigmas[-1][agent.X_idx[-1]] 
                #V[agent] = math.sqrt(agent.beta) * agent.sigma[agent.proposed] # !!!!!!!!!!
                #V[agent] = math.sqrt(agent.beta) * agent.sigma[agent.X_idx[-2]]
                                
            average_V = np.mean(V.values())
                
            V_filtered = {}
            for agent in V:
                if V[agent] >= average_V:
                    V_filtered[agent] = agent.proposed_score - max(agent.T)
                    
            if len(V_filtered) == 0: 
                V_filtered = V
            
            if len(V) != 0:
                
                #print V_filtered
                choosen = max(V_filtered, key=V_filtered.get)
                self.choosen_idx = self.agents.index(choosen)
                choosen.execute(True)
            
        self.t = self.t + 1
    
    def report(self):
        sum_regret = 0.0
        sum_max_acc = 0.0
        sum_min_acc_loss = 0.0
        
        for agent in self.agents:
            if len(agent.T) == 0:
                base_accuracy = min(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                max_possible_acc = max(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                sum_regret = sum_regret + max_possible_acc - base_accuracy           
                sum_max_acc = sum_max_acc + base_accuracy
                sum_min_acc_loss = sum_min_acc_loss + max_possible_acc - base_accuracy
            else:
                max_possible_acc = max(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                sum_regret = sum_regret + max_possible_acc - agent.T[-1]            
                sum_max_acc = sum_max_acc + max(agent.T)
                sum_min_acc_loss = sum_min_acc_loss + max_possible_acc - max(agent.T)

        return self.choosen_idx, sum_regret, sum_max_acc, sum_min_acc_loss

class RRUCBAgent:
    
    def __init__(self, agents):
        self.agents = agents
        self.n_agents = len(agents)
        self.t = 0
        self.choosen_idx = None
    
    def execute(self):
        
        it = 0
        while True:
            it = it + 1
            if it > 2 * self.n_agents: break
            agent = self.agents[self.t % self.n_agents]
            agent.propose_next()
            if agent.proposed == None: 
                self.t = self.t + 1
                continue
            agent.execute(True)
            self.choosen_idx = self.t % self.n_agents
            self.t = self.t + 1
            break
        
    def report(self):
        sum_regret = 0.0
        sum_max_acc = 0.0
        sum_min_acc_loss = 0.0
        
        for agent in self.agents:
            if len(agent.T) == 0:
                base_accuracy = min(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                max_possible_acc = max(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                sum_regret = sum_regret + max_possible_acc - base_accuracy           
                sum_max_acc = sum_max_acc + base_accuracy
                sum_min_acc_loss = sum_min_acc_loss + max_possible_acc - base_accuracy
            else:
                max_possible_acc = max(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                sum_regret = sum_regret + max_possible_acc - agent.T[-1]            
                sum_max_acc = sum_max_acc + max(agent.T)
                sum_min_acc_loss = sum_min_acc_loss + max_possible_acc - max(agent.T)

        return self.choosen_idx, sum_regret, sum_max_acc, sum_min_acc_loss
    
class RandomUCBAgent:
    
    def __init__(self, agents):
        self.agents = agents
        self.n_agents = len(agents)
        self.t = 0
        self.choosen_idx = None
    
    def execute(self):
        
        if self.t < 2 * self.n_agents: # first two rounds, do round robin
            agent = self.agents[self.t % self.n_agents]
            agent.propose_next()
            agent.execute(True)
            self.t = self.t + 1
        else:        
            it = 0
            while True:
                it = it + 1
                if it > 2 * self.n_agents: break

                self.choosen_idx = random.randint(0, self.n_agents - 1)
                agent = self.agents[self.choosen_idx]
                agent.propose_next()
                if agent.proposed == None:
                    continue

                agent.execute(True)
                self.t = self.t + 1
                break
        
    def report(self):
        sum_regret = 0.0
        sum_max_acc = 0.0
        sum_min_acc_loss = 0.0
        
        for agent in self.agents:
            if len(agent.T) == 0:
                base_accuracy = min(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                max_possible_acc = max(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                sum_regret = sum_regret + max_possible_acc - base_accuracy           
                sum_max_acc = sum_max_acc + base_accuracy
                sum_min_acc_loss = sum_min_acc_loss + max_possible_acc - base_accuracy
            else:
                max_possible_acc = max(map(lambda o: o.observe(), agent.objects))
                sum_regret = sum_regret + max_possible_acc - agent.T[-1]            
                sum_max_acc = sum_max_acc + max(agent.T)
                sum_min_acc_loss = sum_min_acc_loss + max_possible_acc - max(agent.T)

        return self.choosen_idx, sum_regret, sum_max_acc, sum_min_acc_loss

class Model:
    def __init__(self, feature, v):
        self.features = feature
        self.value = v

    def observe(self):
        return self.value

def init_ucbs():
    global data
    global train
    global test
    global delta
    ucbs = []
    for i in range(0, nucbs):
        objects = []
        for j in range(0, NMODEL):            
            model = Model(data[train, j], data[test[i], j])
            objects.append(model)
        ucbs.append(UCBAgent(objects, delta))
    return ucbs

            data = data / np.amax(data)

            ########## RUN ############

                        randommin_acc_loss_agg.append(sum_min_acc_loss + randommin_acc_loss_agg[-1])

                sum_multiregrets = sum_multiregrets + multiregrets    
                sum_multimin_acc_loss = sum_multimin_acc_loss + multimin_acc_loss
